件出？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWWDC 2008: iPhone 3G<br />\nWWDC 2009: iPhone 3GS, new MacBook Pro<br />\nWWDC 2010: iPhone 4<br />\nWWDC 2012: MacBook Pro with Retina display<br />\nWWDC 2013: Max Pro, MacBook Air <br />\n<br />\n對上十年有五年都有新硬件<br />\n加上今年好多product line 都係時候update <br />\niMac, MacBook, iPad Pro, wifi base station ....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n謝謝更正。<br />\n但近年Developers Conference好似真係講專講 OS 同出Beta 比Developer. <br />\n部iPad 同Air 都好慢，希望真係有新iPad Pro 同平價版 MacBook出。<br />\n<br />\n其實我由 iPhone 1 就開始用Apple d 嘢。仲記得當年叫友人係美國買番來比我，雖然 JB 先用到仲要2G. 最初甚至連Store同App 都無，但開箱果時真係開心同興奮。</blockquote><br />\n得啦，係啦，明啦，ok啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfffc7b3e9a1400cc99b1468d96cff0564ca39e","tid":265524,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:35:28.000Z","msg":"屌幾時出新iMac 而家個spec連i7都無<br />\n唔夠我用"},{"pid":"6671f31c652eb6963d30c967a0c543ab72eec836","tid":265524,"uid":6587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:41:24.000Z","msg":"我估個 siri 喇叭，應該會做埋router"},{"pid":"e48a68989477483bff16665e424ad07af3062386","tid":265524,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:47:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌幾時出新iMac 而家個spec連i7都無<br />\n唔夠我用</blockquote><br />\n我都等緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望有新設計啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21045cd5492a688715f658d2b9f470f2c644aa96","tid":265524,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T23:44:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢係咪以為樓主想打倒數變左程序表？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/1